OL,3,C'Life changing': Londonderry pensioner
OL,4,Cawarded #1m after infected blood
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,FA pensioner from Londonderry who
OL,8,Fcontracted hepatitis C from
OL,9,Fcontaminated blood more than 50 years
OL,10,Fago is to receive more than #1m
OL,11,Fcompensation, it was announced on
OL,12,FFriday.
OL,14,FThe man, who is not being named,
OL,15,Fsecured the payout in a settlement
OL,16,Freached with the body overseeing
OL,17,Fclaims by thousands of victims across
OL,18,Fthe UK.
OL,20,FHis lawyers described the outcome as
OL,21,F"life changing".
