OL,3,C'Life changing': Londonderry pensioner
OL,4,Cawarded #1m after infected blood
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,FThe 67-year-old man suffers from
OL,8,Fhaemophilia - a rare condition which
OL,9,Faffects the ability of blood to clot.
OL,11,FDuring the early 1970s he received
OL,12,Fblood infected by viruses which led to
OL,13,Fhim developing hepatitis C.
OL,15,FThousands of others with bleeding
OL,16,Fdisorders were also given contaminated
OL,17,Ftransfusions.
