OL,3,C'Life changing': Londonderry pensioner
OL,4,Cawarded #1m after infected blood
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,FIn May last year the Infected Blood
OL,8,FCompensation Authority (IBCA) was
OL,9,Festablished to deal with claims made
OL,10,Fby victims of the scandal.
OL,12,FBelfast-based legal firm KRW Law, who
OL,13,Frepresent the man, confirmed his
OL,14,Fapplication has now been fully settled.
OL,16,FSolicitor Owen Winters disclosed that
OL,17,Fa figure of just over #1m is to be
OL,18,Fpaid out to him.
