OL,3,C'Life changing': Londonderry pensioner
OL,4,Cawarded #1m after infected blood
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,F"To say this sum of money is life
OL,8,Fchanging is somewhat bittersweet given
OL,9,Fthat our client has lived with this
OL,10,Fhorrendous condition for most of his
OL,11,Flife," Mr Winters said.
OL,13,FThe lawyer also suggested there has
OL,14,Fbeen some frustration over the time
OL,15,Ftaken to fully roll out the
OL,16,Fcompensation scheme.
OL,18,F"Some of the infected are worried that
OL,19,Fthey may not live long enough to see
OL,20,Ftheir applications through to
OL,21,Fconclusion," he added.
